title: Vixen - Kendra Sunderland, Alexa Grace (Lets Share My Boyfriend)
description:
Kendra's parents have gone away for the weekend and she has invited her boyfriend Jack over. It's his birthday and she has a special surprise for him. He is pretty experimental, and has always wanted a threesome with another girl, so Kendra has got her best friend Alexa in on the plan. After chilling for a while and having a few drinks, Kendra blindfolds Jack and tells him his birthday surprise is ready. When the blindfold is removed, he realises that this birthday is certainly going to be one to remember.
